name: Architectural_Wall_Cabinet,_Whitewashed_Finish
reviews: couldn't be happier, purchased two for my new home and they look fabulous!
Love it! Perfect for my bathroom.
I got exactly what I was expecting.

This is a perfect accent piece. It was very difficult to hang because there are metal nail slots in all 4 corners and it takes extreme patience to line them all up exactly. Also it would be more sturdy if you could use screws with anchors but alas the nail head slots do not accommodate any size of screw heads...therefore this cabinet has to be mostly decorative, not functional.
This item arrived promptly, and in excellent condition. I was looking for a small yet unique cabinet for my apartment bathroom. It's perfect!!
